Package org.apache.gora.tutorial.log

This package contains official tutorial related all classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistributedLogManager
    DistributedLogManager DistributedLogManager is the tutorial class to illustrate the basic distributed features that can be gained when persistent dataStore is used together with cache dataStore similar to JCacheStore.
    KeyValueWritable<K extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,V extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable>
    A WritableComparable containing a key-value WritableComparable pair.
    LogAnalytics
    LogAnalytics is the tutorial class to illustrate Gora MapReduce API.
    LogAnalytics.LogAnalyticsMapper
    The Mapper takes Long keys and Pageview objects, and emits tuples of <url, day> as keys and 1 as values.
    LogAnalytics.LogAnalyticsReducer
    The Reducer receives tuples of <url, day> as keys and a list of values corresponding to the keys, and emits a combined keys and MetricDatum objects.
    LogAnalyticsSpark
    LogAnalyticsSpark is the tutorial class to illustrate Gora Spark API.
    LogManager
    LogManager is the tutorial class to illustrate the basic DataStore API usage.
    TextLong
    A KeyValueWritable of Text keys and LongWritable values.
